Rub the mackerel pieces with the turmeric and curry powder.Heat the vegetable oil in a frying pan over a medium heat. Add the mackerel and fry for two minutes on each side.To make the horseradish cream, place all the ingredients into a small bowl and mix together well.To serve, place the spiced mackerel fillets onto a bed of rocket with a spoonful of the horseradish cream on the side.